# ExcelExamples

This repository contains ready-to run examples to showcase the Modelon Impact Add-In for Excel.

## Getting started

To run the examples, you need to

- Download the Modelon Impact workspace [ExcelDemo](https://impact.modelon.cloud/hub/user-redirect/impact/customizations/workspace_management/index.html?)
- Install the Modelon Impact Excel add-in (instructions available in <https://help.modelon.com/>)
- Open an Excel sheet in the ExcelSheets directory to run it using the Modelon Impact Excel Add-In

Available examples:

- SimpleBatteryCharging
